short.ar: مع Aircraft Combat 2 ، تخلص من الأعداء وحاول الحصول على أعلى الدرجات دون تحطم.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Are you ready to blow up warplanes with a mini plane! Use your best tactics and smash all planes in the challenging and snowy section.

How To Play
Played with Mouse-Space Key.

Aircraft Combat 2 Game Features
✓ Cartoon graphics
✓ Realistic rocket system
✓ Extreme warplanes
✓ Fun snow level
✓ Realistic damage

Finally, you can enjoy these game for free (and more requests will be added)! Aircraft Combat 2 Game extension does not contain any hidden ads.
